JSCasts
SUBSCRIBE
JSCasts - Get access to best source of JavaScript knowledge and skills! JSCasts are produced by the Software Brothers CTO - Wojtek Krysiak, who is also responsible for open-software projects like AdminBro and better-docs. The goal of running the channel is to provide a place where JavaScript developers around the world can check out new libraries and processes in a regular fashion.Free episodes are released two times a month, on Tuesdays and Thursdays. Screencasts are concise and touch one specific topic which could be a particular JavaScript library or programming technique. You'll find lots of practical JavaScript tutorials, hacks and useful tricks. Target audience is intermediate JavaScript developers but both junior and senior developers will find interesting things here as well. Text version of the casts is always available on SoftwareBrothers blog. So if you prefer reading instead of watching - check it out! Thanks for being here! Enjoy!
